"2 teaspoons sherry vinegar","2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","  Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper","3  endives (about 1 lb. total), halved and sliced into 1/2-inch half-moons (about 5 cups)","1 cup parsley leaves (from about 1/4 bunch)","2  firm but ripe pears, cut into quarters, cored and sliced (about 3 cups)","1/2 cup chopped pecans, toasted","1  4-oz. wedge blue cheese, sliced"